    "Se-lectiveContext does not rely on external models or additional parameters, and can be applied to any model architecture.",
    "However, there are two main disadvantages: (1) It relies on accurate phrase boundary detection using SpaCy.",
    "(2) Currently, there are no methods for merging verb phrases.",
    "Figure 3: Architectures for various prompt compression models by hard prompt methods.",
    "For SelectiveContext and LLMLingua, the bottom language models filter the prompt tokens without modifying them, serving as selection mechanisms."
